              "reference": "2 Corinthians 4:17-18",
              "theme": "Hope",
              "text": "For our light affliction, which is but for a moment, is working for us a far more exceeding and eternal weight of glory, while we do not look at the things which are seen, but at the things which are not seen. For the things which are seen are temporary, but the things which are not seen are eternal."
            },
