              "reference": "1 Peter 1:3-4",
              "theme": "Hope",
              "text": "Blessed be the God and Father of our Lord Jesus Christ, who according to His abundant mercy has begotten us again to a living hope through the resurrection of Jesus Christ from the dead, to an inheritance incorruptible and undefiled and that does not fade away, reserved in heaven for you,"
            },
            {
              "label": "Next week",
              "date": "7/5",
              "reference": "1 Peter 3:15-16",
              "theme": "Hope",
              "text": "But sanctify the Lord God in your hearts, and always be ready to give a defense to everyone who asks you a reason for the hope that is in you, with meekness and fear; having a good conscience, that when they defame you as evildoers, those who revile your good conduct in Christ may be ashamed."
            }
          ]
